title: [PS3] PDC World Championship Darts: Pro Tour
description:
Capture the passion and excitement of darts in your living room.

* Take part in an authentic darts experience with your family and friends using PlayStation Move.
* Enjoy new commentary and new players including Simon Whitlock, Mervin King and Colin Osborne.
* Get as close to the action as possible in tournaments such as The Grand Slam of Darts and the European Championship.
